COGILOG (https://www.cogilog.com) | Mac Developers | Toulouse, France | Onsite | Full-time

We are looking for 2 Mac developers to join our team in Toulouse, France.

Key Qualifications: Experience in developing Mac or iOS apps, Xcode, Objective-C, fluent in French.

COGILOG develops accounting, invoicing and payroll applications for small businesses in France.

For more information, visit www.cogilog.com/Offres-emploi.html
